- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is a possible category as the paper discusses the characterization of users in online communities, which can be seen as a human-computer interaction problem. 
- cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with analyzing user behavior in online communities, which can have implications for cybersecurity.
